Report Overview¶

This is to report the Megalectrics sales for the year of 2020

Dataset Overview¶

There are 187 datas in the dataset with 17 features (STATION_NAMES, JAN_2020, FEB_2020, MAR_2020, TOTAL_1ST_QUARTER, APR_2020, MAY_2020, JUNE_2020, TOTAL_2ND_QUARTER, JULY_2020, AUG_2020, SEP_2020, TOTAL_3RD_QUARTER, OCT_2020, NOV_2020, DEC_2020, TOTAL_4TH_QUARTER).

2020 MONTHLY SALES¶

We visualized each sale by month and each station across the board. Our observation was that out of all the stations across the board CLASSIC FM Lagos was outstanding, followed by BEAT FM Lagos. The remaining stations have fairly sales throughout each month. In some months stations like NAIJA FM Lagos, NAIJA FM PH and LAGOSTALKS FM fair more than other stations apart from CLASSIC FM Lagos and BEAT FM Lagos.

2020 QUARTERLY SALES¶

For Quarterly sales, we visualized each sale by 1st, 2nd, 3rd, and 4th quarter for each station across the board. Our observation was that out of all the stations across the board CLASSIC FM Lagos was outstanding throughout all the Quarters, followed by BEAT FM Lagos. The remaining stations have fairly sales throughout each quarter.

2020 SALES BY LOCATIONS¶

Here we visualized each sale by locations (LAGOS, IBADAN, PORT-HARCOURT, AND ABUJA)for each station across the board. Our observation for the Lagos location shows that CLASSIC FM Lagos sales were much more outstanding than the rest stations in Lagos. For Ibadan location BEAT FM Ibadan performed better than NAIJA FM Ibadan. For the Port-Harcourt location NAIJA FM PH edge other stations. In Abuja location BEAT FM Abuja also performed better than CLASSIC FM Abuja.

2020 AVERAGE SALES PER YEAR¶

We find the average sales for the year 2020 on all stations across the board. We have observed CLASSIC FM Lagos has an average sales of 24,126,090.00. BEAT FM Lagos has an average sales of 20,046,060.00. LagosTalks has an average sales of 3,194,836.00. Also, CLASSIC FM Abuja has the lowest average sales of 445,397.60.

In [211]:
avg_salesnew1.plot.bar(x="STATION_NAMES", y="average_sales", figsize = (15,8), color = 'black')
plt.bar(avg_salesnew1['STATION_NAMES'], avg_salesnew1['average_sales'], color = 'black', alpha = 0.5);
plt.title('2020 AVERAGE SALES PER YEAR', fontsize = 20);
plt.xlabel('Station Names', fontsize = 20, labelpad=15);
plt.ylabel('Average Sales', fontsize = 20, labelpad=15);

Conclusion¶

The total sales for the year 2020 are 700,171,559.74. CLASSIC FM Lagos's total sales for the year 2020 is 289,513,122.65 and BEAT FM Lagos's total sales for the year 2020 is 240,552,741.47. The remaining stations such as LAGOSTALKS FM, NAIJA FM Lagos, BEAT FM Ibadan, NAIJA FM Ibadan, BEAT FM PH, CLASSIC FM PH, NAIJA FM PH, BEAT FM Abuja, and CLASSIC FM Abuja all shares the total sales of 170,105,695.62 for the year 2020.
